name: Ojeda Bread #6
description:
The sixth in a weekly series combining baking + drawing.

Over the past year, one of the constants in my life has been baking a weekly sourdough loaf for my family. I wanted to pair that consistency with my artistic practice.

A new "pan" is usually baked on Thursday evenings. New drawing to follow soon after. 

Previous drawings can be found on Foundation & Rarible.
